html:
{% set current_date = frappe.utils.nowdate() %}
{% set formatted_date = frappe.utils.get_datetime(current_date).strftime("%e %B %Y") %}
{% set promotion_date = frappe.utils.get_datetime(doc.promotion_date).strftime("%e %B %Y") %}

<p><b>Date: </b>{{ formatted_date or '' }}</p>

<p class="space">Dear<br/>
{{doc.employee}} ({{doc.employee_name}})<br/>
{{doc.custom_designation}}</p>
<h4>Sub: Promotion</h4>
{% set first_transfer_detail = doc.promotion_details[0] if doc.promotion_details and doc.promotion_details|length > 0 else None %}
{% set transfer_new_field_value = first_transfer_detail.new if first_transfer_detail else 'No any new position' %}
<p>You performance and over all efforts in improving the productivity of the mines have been appraised for the year 2019-20 and management is pleased to
promote you to the position of <b>{{ transfer_new_field_value }}</b> W.e.f {{ promotion_date or '' }} and also to revise your salary as under:</p>
{% set employee_doc = frappe.get_doc("Employee", doc.employee) %}
<table border="1" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <th width="40%">Salary Component</th>
        <th width="30%">Present Salary</th>
        <th width="30%">Revised Salary</th>
    </tr>
{% set a = namespace(count=0) %}
    {% for earning in employee_doc.custom_earnings %}
        {% set revised_earning = doc.custom_earnings | selectattr("salary_component", "equalto", earning.salary_component) | first %}
        <tr>
            {% set a.count = a.count + earning.amount %}
            <td>{{ earning.salary_component }}</td>
            <td style="text-align: right;">{{ earning.get_formatted("amount") if earning.amount else "0" }}</td>
            <td style="text-align: right;">{{ revised_earning.get_formatted("amount") if revised_earning else "0" }}</td>
        </tr>
    {% endfor %}
{% set b = namespace(count=0) %}
    {% for earning in doc.custom_earnings %}
        {% if not employee_doc.custom_earnings | selectattr("salary_component", "equalto", earning.salary_component) | first %}
            <tr>
                {% set b.count = b.count + earning.amount %}
                <td>{{ earning.salary_component }}</td>
                <td style="text-align: right;">0</td>
                <td style="text-align: right;">{{ earning.get_formatted("amount") }}</td>
            </tr>
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    <tr>
        <td style="n:right"><b>Gross Salary</b></td>
        <td style="text-align: right;"><b>{{ a.count }}</b></td>
        <td style="text-align: right;"><b>{{b.count}}</b></td>
    </tr>
</table>
<p>We hope while appreciating the gesture of good will of the management you will continue to make your all out efforts towards the growth of the company.</p>
<p>Best wishes</p>

<p class="signature"><b>Authorized Signatory</b></p>
